as_tibble

Source: R/as_tibble.R
as_tibble-methods.Rd

Coerce an CoverageExperiment or AggregatedCoverage object into a tibble

Usage

# S3 method for class 'AggregatedCoverage'
as_tibble(x, ...)

Arguments

x

an CoverageExperiment object

...

ignored

Value

tibble

Examples

data(ac)
as_tibble(ac)
